          "note": "No. 4 - her nephew Jack clicked with it around age two, once he understood what toys are."
        },
        {
          "title": "Matilda",
          "year": 1996,
          "note": "No. 5 - her favorite book as a kid, and one of the rare adaptations that matched what she'd pictured."
        }
